cellularData

Class Country

  • java.lang.Object
    • cellularData.Country

  • public class Country
extends java.lang.Object
    One object of this class represents a single country. Each country has a string name and an array of SubscriptionYear that holds all the years and cellular data for each year.
    Author:
    Zach Rooney
